OL,3,CHeathrow issues warning over impact of
OL,4,CMiddle East war
OL,6,FHeathrow airport has warned it expects
OL,7,Fits passenger numbers for the rest of
OL,8,Fthe year to be affected by the
OL,9,Fsituation in the Middle East.
OL,11,FSome 18.9 million people passed
OL,12,Fthrough its four terminals during the
OL,13,Ffirst three months of the year.
OL,15,FThis was a year-on-year increase of
OL,16,F3.7%, which the airport said was
OL,17,Fbecause it "temporarily absorbed
OL,18,Fdemand from elsewhere".
OL,26,@yD@LOUzD@VO]
