OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777532747
OL,3,CHeathrow issues warning over impact of
OL,4,CMiddle East war
OL,6,FAbout half a million passengers per
OL,7,Fday usually use airports in Dubai,
OL,8,FDoha or Abu Dhabi, which are vital
OL,9,Fhubs for travel between Europe and the
OL,10,Fcontinents of Asia and Australia.
OL,12,FAirspace closures following the
OL,13,Foutbreak of the war in the Middle East
OL,14,Fon February 28 had a major impact on
OL,15,Fair travel.
OL,17,FMuch of the region's airspace has
OL,18,Fsince reopened, but many people are
OL,19,Favoiding flying there because of the
OL,20,Fwar.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
