FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777532747
OL,3,CHeathrow issues warning over impact of
OL,4,CMiddle East war
OL,6,FHeathrow's warning comes after ITV
OL,7,FNews exclusively revealed that
OL,8,Fairlines have asked the government for
OL,9,Femergency support in order to protect
OL,10,Fbusiness travel, holiday traffic and
OL,11,Ffreight operations,
OL,13,FEarlier this month ITV News was given
OL,14,Faccess to a confidential briefing
OL,15,Fdocument submitted to ministers and
OL,16,Fthe regulator, the Civil Aviation
OL,17,FAuthority (CAA), warning that if the
OL,18,Fdisruption "continues or worsens", it
OL,19,Fwill force airlines to cut flights and
OL,20,Fpush up fares.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
