PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777532747
OL,3,CHeathrow issues warning over impact of
OL,4,CMiddle East war
OL,6,FIn a trading update on Wednesday,
OL,7,FHeathrow said: "While Heathrow has
OL,8,Ftemporarily absorbed demand from
OL,9,Felsewhere, passenger numbers for the
OL,10,Frest of the year are likely to be
OL,11,Fimpacted whilst there is significant
OL,12,Funcertainty in the Middle East."
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Sally Ding, Heathrow's
OL,15,Fchief financial officer, declared the
OL,16,Fairport is ready to go ahead with its
OL,17,Fplan to build a third runway "with the
OL,18,Fright regulatory framework and
OL,19,FGovernment policy in place".
OL,26,@oD@POUtD@`O]yD@^OU{D@[O]
