PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777532747
OL,3,CHeathrow issues warning over impact of
OL,4,CMiddle East war
OL,6,FShe said Heathrow is currently "full",
OL,7,Fwhich means "fewer choices and higher
OL,8,Ffares for passengers, and missed
OL,9,Fopportunities for the UK economy".
OL,11,FHeathrow's first-quarter revenue
OL,12,Fincreased by 2.3% from a year ago to
OL,13,F#844 million, amid rises in passenger
OL,14,Fnumbers, food and beverage sales and
OL,15,Fuptake of premium services.
OL,17,FBut its adjusted operating costs were
OL,18,F6.5% higher, driven by an uptick in
OL,19,Fwages and national insurance payments,
OL,20,FIT investments and the number of
OL,21,Fpassengers requiring support.
OL,26,@nD@`OUnD@eO]oD@MOUqD@aO]
